            "category_title": "Product & materials",
            "category_anchor": "materials",
            "question": "What materials do you use?",
            "answer": "<ul><li><strong>Organic canvas:</strong> a sturdy cotton textile grown without harmful chemicals</li><li><strong>Jute:</strong> a rain-fed, low-impact fiber</li><li><strong>Juco:</strong> a woven blend of jute and cotton that balances structure and softness</li></ul>"
          }
        },
