          "settings": {
            "category_number": "02",
            "category_title": "Product & materials",
            "category_anchor": "materials",
            "question": "Is your packaging eco-friendly?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Our packaging is recyclable and plastic-free. We use:</p><ul><li>Recycled paper boxes</li><li>Water-activated paper tape</li><li>Algae ink (carbon-negative) for printing</li></ul><p>Every element is chosen to minimize waste while protecting your bag in transit.</p>"
          }
        },
