            "answer": "<ul><li><strong>Jute:</strong> grows with minimal water and no pesticides</li><li><strong>Organic cotton:</strong> preserves soil health and reduces runoff</li><li><strong>Juco:</strong> offers breathability, strength, and natural beauty - well-suited to lasting design</li></ul>"
